{"title":"海歌","authors":["陈燕妮"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":8,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"海歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈燕妮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我托举太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑重地交给早晨第一缕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升起的炊烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和昨天一同诞生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把弄潮人的长长故事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和早已封冻了的岁月锁进记忆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依我与历史的契约和誓言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并且，默默唱着给山的情歌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们相见在白天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相思却在黑夜。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我以我的柔弱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一任小川注入我的肌肤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的胸怀，听凭裁剪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一个收获的季节，都微笑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏上我的双肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然而，我渴望同真正的力士角逐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从容地在礁石上镌刻我的威望。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同时与桅杆对峙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把丈夫出海的渔号"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"描上妻子的双眼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我疲倦时，会唱歌的孩子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都会跑来—捡拾我匆忙中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗落海滩的句号。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"然后把整个夏天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉入我的风景线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我体味着地壳的错位"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和岩浆的躁动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从最初的开始，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直至最后的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从时代直至蓝天。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}